96#define AM_HAL_IOM_PAUSE_FLAG_RESV (IOM0_CQPAUSEEN_CQPEN_SWFLAGEN7 | IOM0_CQPAUSEEN_CQPEN_SWFLAGEN6 | IOM0_CQPAUSEEN_CQPEN_SWFLAGEN5)
97#define AM_HAL_IOM_SC_RESV_MASK (AM_HAL_IOM_PAUSE_FLAG_RESV | (AM_HAL_IOM_PAUSE_FLAG_RESV << 8) | (AM_HAL_IOM_PAUSE_FLAG_RESV << 16))
98
99// We use SWFLAGEN7 to control SW pausing Command Queue - default unPause
100// We use SWFLAGEN6 to pause on the sequece loopback - default Pause
101#define AM_HAL_IOM_PAUSE_FLAG_IDX (_VAL2FLD(IOM0_CQPAUSEEN_CQPEN, IOM0_CQPAUSEEN_CQPEN_IDXEQ))
102#define AM_HAL_IOM_PAUSE_FLAG_CQ (_VAL2FLD(IOM0_CQPAUSEEN_CQPEN, IOM0_CQPAUSEEN_CQPEN_SWFLAGEN7))
103#define AM_HAL_IOM_PAUSE_FLAG_SEQLOOP (_VAL2FLD(IOM0_CQPAUSEEN_CQPEN, IOM0_CQPAUSEEN_CQPEN_SWFLAGEN6))
104#define AM_HAL_IOM_PAUSE_FLAG_BLOCK (_VAL2FLD(IOM0_CQPAUSEEN_CQPEN, IOM0_CQPAUSEEN_CQPEN_SWFLAGEN5))
105
106// By default - we Pause CQ for no more entries, or force pause from SW
107#define AM_HAL_IOM_PAUSE_DEFAULT AM_HAL_IOM_PAUSE_FLAG_IDX
108#define AM_HAL_IOM_CQP_PAUSE_DEFAULT (AM_HAL_IOM_PAUSE_FLAG_IDX | AM_HAL_IOM_PAUSE_FLAG_CQ)
